<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fs-4" href="/">SAJAG</a>
            <div class="d-flex">
                <a href="/api/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2">Login</a>
                <a href="/api/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
        <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">SAJAG: Proactive Disaster Readiness for a Resilient India</h1>
                <p class="lead">Moving beyond fragmented data to a unified, intelligent platform for monitoring, assessing, and predicting disaster management training needs across the nation.</p>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
                    <a href="/public-map" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">View Preparedness Map</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="featured-3">
        <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Our Key Features</h2>
        <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
            <div class="feature col">
                <h3 class="fs-2">Real-time GIS Monitoring</h3>
                <p>Visualize all training activities on a national map. Track coverage across geography, themes, and institutions in real-time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature col">
                <h3 class="fs-2">Impact via Readiness Score</h3>
                <p>Measure the true effectiveness of training programs with our post-assessment system, providing a quantitative "Readiness Score" for every participant, district, and state.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature col">
                <h3 class="fs-2">Predictive Gap Analysis</h3>
                <p>Our system proactively identifies high-risk districts with low preparedness, guiding NDMA to focus their training efforts where they are needed most.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>